                    <ul>
                        <li>Balance <strong>animals vs creatures</strong> (more passive wildlife, fewer monsters)</li>
                        <li>Make <strong>dangerous creatures rare</strong> in common areas</li>
                        <li>Use <strong>water spawns</strong> for sea serpents, kraken, water elementals</li>
                        <li><strong>Desert</strong> should have heat-resistant creatures</li>
                        <li><strong>Snow/Ice</strong> areas need cold-adapted spawns</li>
                    </ul>

